{"tid":1543331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(好準) 解簽人陳天恩指劉業強所求「中籤」乃下籤「非常差 林鄭來年有好日子過 斬我個頭當凳坐」","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T11:46:08.000Z","uid":124914,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e25479bbba9a5929acee6dde7b1c293e9444a4cc","tid":1543331,"uid":124914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CBTa_GBdt7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCBTa_GBdt7w&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=06908b5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CBTa_GBdt7w</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年2月6日<br />\n新界鄉議局主席劉業強大年初二在車公廟為香港求得八十六籤「中籤」，籤文為「石田為業喜非常，畫餅將來未見香，怎曉田耕耘不得，那知餅食不充腸」，解曰「出入謹慎，家宅不吉，自身平安，求財不遂」。劉業強希望市民減少爭拗支持政府。解籤師父認為該籤是「望梅止渴」的中下籤，寓意香港來年非常差，尤其是對特首林鄭月娥尤其不利。<br />\n<br />\n求左支咁既籤，劉業強會否被犬決？<br />\n另外佢果句希望市民減少爭拗支持政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天佑香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f25f81a19ab2cd067d527e418f38b6da850c2542","tid":1543331,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https:/